subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Eun-Hee Ji earned her first victory on the L.P.G.A. Tour, rallying for a two-stroke win over Suzann Pettersen at the Wegmans L.P.G.A. in Pittsford, N.Y. Ji, a 22-year-old from South Korea, shot a five-under 67, and Pettersen shot a 72 and surrendered a three-stroke lead.
